      "effect": "If this card is Normal or Special Summoned: You can activate 1 of these effects;\n\u25cf Add 1 \"Zubaba\" monster from your Deck to your hand, except \"Zubababa Knight\", and if you do, this card's Level becomes that added monster's.\n\u25cf Destroy 1 Level 4 or lower Defense Position monster your opponent controls.\nIf this card is detached from an Xyz Monster to activate that monster's effect: You can add 1 \"Gagaga\" monster from your Deck to your hand. You can only use each effect of \"Zubababa Knight\" once per turn.",
